---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Recipes | Makeaway</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Simple recipes, camp cooking ideas, homestead meals, and practical food notes from Makeaway."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <a class="back-link" href="/">← Back to home</a>

      <p class="eyebrow">Makeaway</p>

      <h1>Recipes</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        Simple meals, camp cooking, homestead recipes, and practical food ideas
        for eating well without making life more complicated.
      </p>

      <!-- Recipe cards: add each new recipe or cooking resource here -->
      <section class="recipe-grid">
        <a class="recipe-card" href="/articles/cast-iron-campfire-breakfast">
          <span>Camp Cooking</span>
          <h2>Cast Iron Campfire Breakfast</h2>
          <p>
            A simple skillet breakfast idea for camping, camper life, or slow
            weekend mornings.
          </p>
        </a>

        <a class="recipe-card" href="/articles/basic-homestead-chili">
          <span>Homestead Meal</span>
          <h2>Basic Homestead Chili</h2>
          <p>
            A hearty, flexible meal that works for meal prep, cold nights, and
            feeding a group.
          </p>
        </a>

        <a class="recipe-card" href="/articles/chuck-box-meal-ideas">
          <span>Camp Setup</span>
          <h2>Chuck Box Meal Ideas</h2>
          <p>
            Easy meals to keep in rotation when cooking from a camper, campsite,
            or outdoor kitchen box.
          </p>
        </a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    color: #f5f1e8;
    background: #172117;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(124, 185, 9, 0.22), transparent 35%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #111811, #0c2002);
  }

  main {
    width: min(980px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 0 96px;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    color: #c9d8a6;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #c9d8a6;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.07em;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 30px 0 0;
    color: #ded8c8;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.45rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .recipe-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 72px;
  }

  .recipe-card,
  .recipe-card:visited {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.18);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 34px;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition:
      transform 180ms ease,
      border-color 180ms ease,
      background 180ms ease,
      box-shadow 180ms ease;
  }

  .recipe-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: rgba(201, 216, 166, 0.7);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
  }

  .recipe-card span {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    color: #c9d8a6;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .recipe-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 760px;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .recipe-card p {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 20px 0 0;
    color: #d5ccb8;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    main {
      padding: 56px 0 80px;
    }

    .recipe-card,
    .recipe-card:visited {
      padding: 26px;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }

    .recipe-card h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 12vw, 3.3rem);
    }
  }
</style>
